<paragraph id="CF1136AEFFE5FFFFFF695022FB7E29B2" blockId="26.[189,1158,622,649]" box="[189,1158,622,649]" pageId="26" pageNumber="192">Two males: total length 7.8−11.1; prosoma length 3.8−5.3; femur I length 4.4−5.7.</paragraph>
